# App Essentials Rules

## App Essentials Summary

`@/packages/app-essentials` is the core blockchain utility and SDK package within the Frak ecosystem. It offers a robust, type-safe interface for interacting with various smart contracts, managing wallet initialization, configuring blockchain transports, and integrating tightly with off-chain indexers. The package is written in TypeScript and designed to work seamlessly with the Viem library.
